# AI Assistant Configuration Reference

This file provides configuration for AI assistants working with this repository.

## Master Configuration

Please refer to `AGENTS.md` for comprehensive guidelines, coding standards, workflows, and best practices when contributing to this repository.

## Quick Reference

- Repository uses pnpm workspaces
- Build with `just build`, test with `just test`
- Use Wrangler CLI for Cloudflare Workers
- Follow Conventional Commits specification
- Prefer RPC over HTTP for inter-service communication
- Use Hono framework with Zod validation

For complete details, always consult `AGENTS.md`.